New MDASOnline CSV file format specification effective October Cc Bill NonPrivilegedpst Greetings The new CSV file format specification will be posted to the CAISO Internet site at the following address by COB tomorrow docshtml docshtml You may also reach this topic area by going to clientservmetering clientservmetering and clicking on MDAS Online Enhancements The name of the document is MDASOnline Meter Data ExchangeRequest Format CSV Both pdf and rtf formats will be provided Please contact me if you are unable to access this document Please hold any questions you may have about its content until the next TSWG meeting Thanks Leslie Feusi Information Services Application Development Services
